snippet.title: WHAT’S HAPPENING IN DECEMBER FOR YOU?🎄 Pick a Card for the month ahead ❄️
snippet.description:
✨ TIME STAMPS ARE ALSO PINNED IN THE COMMENT SECTION.

READING INTRO — 1:04

✨Pick Your Image✨

1 — 3:20

2 —  27:01

3 — 48:34

❗️FYI❗️

😇 This reading Angel Numbers. Please research the angel numbers for additional messages via whichever source you trust most.  Thank you for watching ☥ 

*** Readings are TIMELESS (whenever the Universe nudges you watch). 

*** Meditate on the thumbnail or pic in the beginning of the video to choose your stack. 

*** Pick one or more stacks if you feel you need to. 

*** Roles can also be reversed/flip-flopped/vice versa/interchangeable. ☥

*** Readings are GENERAL and will not apply to everyone watching. IF IT DOESN’T RESONATE DON’T TRY TO MAKE IT FIT. YOU CAN ALWAYS PICK ANOTHER PILE. AND IF THAT DOESN’T WORK, THIS READING MAY NOT BE FOR YOU. ✌ ☥
